# Create an issue;
# The transitions will appear in the order defined by the opsbar-sequence;
# If you create another issue from the issue view screen, the order will not be respected once you perform a transition.

h3. Expected Results
The order should be respected

h3. Actual Results
Creating an issue from the issue screen, then browsing to this issue will not respect the order.

